{"tid":347283,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入有圖]屙屎屙出血","createTime":"2017-08-04T16:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T10:48:53.000Z","uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d0f697c9002a306b2fb453cc103dbf26f1137d7","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"頭先去廁所屙屎  屙完 發現屎坑鮮紅色 應該血嚟  抹屎見到紙巾都有血<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁以為屙得大力得滯爆肛啦 用塊鏡照嚟睇 菊花淨係損咗少少<br />\n<br />\n照計損咗唔會出咁多血掛 應該係入面出血<br />\n<br />\n而家好撚不安  先得果廿幾歲  是咪有咩暗病 絕症  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人知咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有類似情況嘅巴(絲)打都分享下啦<br />\n<br />\n星期一會去睇醫生  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖(有血冇屎的): <a href=\"https://holland.pk/rivmybz0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frivmybz0&d=QysPipF0KpTl4tUHcs7bb54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=34954bbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://holland.pk/rivmybz0</a>"},{"pid":"2e1b887cc22a1912bf570fa1df346c75a40e7f2d","tid":347283,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"鮮血通常都係肛裂或痔瘡<br />\n唔洗咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d4ab41b6e58590276052e393f9c14142891767","tid":347283,"uid":16666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"普通肛裂姐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食多d高纖維 ，飲地門西梅汁<br />\n<br />\n唔好坐咁多 好返無事"},{"pid":"5791076adcffb0b6148d7406f3a6ad0109739dc5","tid":347283,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78255a4acae35a5388cec69fcefff5f4d69e205c","tid":347283,"uid":16666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:25:18.000Z","msg":"唔需要睇醫生 無藥食<br />\n<br />\n多菜 多纖維食物就解決到"},{"pid":"480b8da09d67d1ff2d22d17a195393130eddab06","tid":347283,"uid":33966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"痛唔痛㗎，體重同埋大便習慣有冇轉變？"},{"pid":"d02fc52a4826da2ee5f2b873c8bffbe2a166e0bf","tid":347283,"uid":106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，前排照左腸鏡好彩只係痔瘡"},{"pid":"1ce14fa1e23309829fca54fc614abf4add169428","tid":347283,"uid":100894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:37:31.000Z","msg":"內痔姐食多啲菜啦"},{"pid":"4bf768b4ed3073482ad11906327e09915c6738c2","tid":347283,"uid":68926,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:39:42.000Z","msg":"如果內臓有事<br />\n啲血唔會鮮紅色"},{"pid":"f13d4461f5b4ce89c1e8fa3fc715ddaba6f9a919","tid":347283,"uid":68926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果內臓有事<br />\n啲血唔會鮮紅色</blockquote><br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"4ef34795c7872060b0e8a7bdb242db61d51352bc","tid":347283,"uid":114294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:14:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果內臓有事<br />\n啲血唔會鮮紅色</blockquote><br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n下消化道有事嘅話都係會鮮紅色"},{"pid":"457395cff62e5241d0f53827d1bde45ab992ebd6","tid":347283,"uid":68926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:15:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果內臓有事<br />\n啲血唔會鮮紅色</blockquote><br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n下消化道有事嘅話都係會鮮紅色</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28496b00702aeaece4aff3756b20bf474e997b82","tid":347283,"uid":129729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲先第一次黎m?"},{"pid":"4a0749545fb13e942f8f66649b651c360b5e6e4b","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痛唔痛㗎，體重同埋大便習慣有冇轉變？</blockquote><br />\n唔痛呀  半年肥咗10磅   平時一日一次 有時會便秘"},{"pid":"3a69c467f0774d8912a3648d51406961bbc866a8","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廿幾歲先第一次黎m?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb4b5b445f64128c00ac1a3f2f1b09b2ef9dca5","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打答我，而家個人都安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以後會食多啲菜纖維同強身健體架啦<br />\n<br />\n希望各位都健康快樂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5e6065af32e397dee5aa6dafe111e672032304","tid":347283,"uid":53292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T20:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位巴打答我，而家個人都安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以後會食多啲菜纖維同強身健體架啦<br />\n<br />\n希望各位都健康快樂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果兩星期內去廁所feel到去唔清 同埋仲有血但唔痛 可能係內痔 就最好照照腸鏡 照個陣會幫你清埋佢 但如果真係有但你放任佢唔理 有機會會變癌"},{"pid":"06ccf5eb8655b9d2a1755aee13ac30467bb1ef02","tid":347283,"uid":92128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:21:47.000Z","msg":"同巴打情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ffd5675b2644949ec3f3a297c85adf549321eab","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝咁多位巴打答我，而家個人都安心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我以後會食多啲菜纖維同強身健體架啦<br />\n<br />\n希望各位都健康快樂  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果兩星期內去廁所feel到去唔清 同埋仲有血但唔痛 可能係內痔 就最好照照腸鏡 照個陣會幫你清埋佢 但如果真係有但你放任佢唔理 有機會會變癌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該巴打 我會留意架啦"},{"pid":"0975a02f5d91650965320858ee898f6d626d24f8","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同巴打情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你見點 有冇痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed9304e14fe85bb4399f7e32b88b126ebd578a44","tid":347283,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c519796856df149281ed176595917b791aca68ef","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T05:48:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肛裂或痔瘡   身體隨年齡增加而下降<br />\n<br />\n慢慢接受啦死老野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38ad31dc074e27afc6774fe1d6f5aa6e54f7237e","tid":347283,"uid":92128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:38:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同巴打情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你見點 有冇痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屙血嗰次唔痛 啱啱再屙一次又正常返"},{"pid":"d22aa7e10cdadfc032cb9f9bf510df418b9e5b92","tid":347283,"uid":7582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:37:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同巴打情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你見點 有冇痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屙血嗰次唔痛 啱啱再屙一次又正常返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我今朝屙都仲有血<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa23d0ef54ba12e48741cd4c9cbd801fd22d650","tid":347283,"uid":1256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"深紅同黑你先驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm